{"tid":969161,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有無知情人解釋點解得m記搞無飲管有d分店死都唔俾 真正搞到客怨氣沖天 fb各種被拒飲管經歷群情洶湧 又唔見其他快餐店咁？","createTime":"2019-01-04T21:05:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-06T03:54:42.000Z","uid":38795,"like":36,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"aa91d8023a6378184965e38f483dc27a8df746ef","tid":969161,"uid":38795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T21:05:03.000Z","msg":"人做無飲管，你做無飲管，點解得麥當勞做得特別乞人憎？<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vKqA4aZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvKqA4aZ.jpg&h=5b98313c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n睇麥當勞上星期個Facebook無飲管post嬲嬲已經多過讚好，群情洶湧中<br />\n留言仲精彩，出現各式各樣被拒攞飲管既經歷<br />\n<br />\n有屌返個客轉頭話佢唔環保既<br />\n有職員攞左出黎經理一手搶返<br />\n有鬼佬就俾本地人就話環保唔俾<br />\n有d求佢咁求先俾<br />\n有d問完唔俾之後又俾<br />\n有d唔俾之後俾兩個杯仔你<br />\n有飲奶昔既見全場有飲管，佢就問極都唔俾<br />\n有大大聲話無飲管<br />\n有寸個客轉頭話你唔知而家日日無飲管<br />\n有上二樓見全場有飲管，佢就問都唔俾<br />\n有d問完話「無論如何」都唔派<br />\n有d員工自已用緊飲管，但同客講唔俾飲管<br />\n<br />\n我食過除麥當勞外所有無飲管既快餐店，問佢攞飲管佢都好爽快咁俾我（大快活直頭放出黎任攞）<br />\n<br />\n唯一一次無飲管後係德福食過一次，問佢攞好快就俾，但睇完fb加連登d消息後已經唔想再去食，因為你唔知間分店會唔會俾飲管，仲要好大機會要發火先有飲管甚至發完都無，直接大幅降低食麥當勞意慾<br />\n<br />\n有無知情人可以解釋下點解得麥當勞可以有d分店死都唔俾，又唔見其他快餐店係咁？得麥當勞搞無飲管真正搞到d食客怨氣沖天？"},{"pid":"c28507cedabbbd1de52efd6be810485cfb837bdc","tid":969161,"uid":152047,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T21:39:12.000Z","msg":"仲要加價<br />\n冇咗飲館冇咗膠袋反而要加價<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真係唔屌唔鬆化<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab081751c9e8716b96b4fbf9cdd6fb28b7772316","tid":969161,"uid":21423,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T21:51:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d29315c61a551993413a1c820781931ede380836","tid":969161,"uid":28279,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T21:53:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 本身麥當勞已經用手食，仲要搶走埋少數僅有既餐具，環保撚正一冚家鏟"},{"pid":"3523db025486d4fd7ef40697c1bda14810ba3b68","tid":969161,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T21:59:37.000Z","msg":"應該係cut cost有bonus"},{"pid":"f40c9b82247bce27fb392e336eb649a183ec9ec3","tid":969161,"uid":183926,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T22:00:37.000Z","msg":"環保撚嘈9老佢麥先迫住走飲筒姐，失驚無神唔俾筒客搏鬧咩<br />\n<br />\n應該上頭講左話一定唔可以亂咁俾<br />\n分店果班又唔同客嘈照俾 先會搞到每間唔同<br />\n<br />\n最on9班環保撚 過撚晒火"},{"pid":"14adc7c110e9724099ff34fd648ea8e352ef637f","tid":969161,"uid":186177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T22:07:55.000Z","msg":"麥記員工係特別低質<br />\n一樣返夜班去做ok 五十幾蚊一個鐘唔好唔好?<br />\n仲要唔使成日有個人指指點點<br />\n<br />\n係呢班員工唔做麥記無其他地方可以做<br />\n麥記又除咗呢班人之外請唔到其他人<br />\n先會養到班人咁串"},{"pid":"c358bc4f73179a7ecf7b7d2bd336eff9f0dc89ab","tid":969161,"uid":224452,"like":6,"dislike":21,"score":-15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T22:25:59.000Z","msg":"從來都係 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>飲筒</strong></span></span>而唔撚係<del><em>飲管</em></del>"},{"pid":"e015cd3f63d94db2bbd038b26ae20d466ca7a69d","tid":969161,"uid":10637,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T22:27:21.000Z","msg":"上次佢死都唔比<br />\n我同個經理講咁我要退錢唔食<br />\n佢話好啊<br />\n當佢想拎現金比我時我話唔得wo<br />\n我要退返落張卡到<br />\n結果未又死死地氣比飲管我"},{"pid":"4e8f35fae84bce817852b7be8a3e1e4a88842860","tid":969161,"uid":23170,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T23:23:34.000Z","msg":"一個10蚊xxxx咪又成堆友走去幫襯，人地根本就無怕過你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67dcbff5ebb055af33407c4ecca9c0ede3ea58a3","tid":969161,"uid":51105,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T23:30:01.000Z","msg":"快啲走埋刀叉羹，好想睇人徒口飲扭扭粉"},{"pid":"3e1c866a0bf8d85c5e4752bb31a047f114d37955","tid":969161,"uid":57376,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"4e8f35fae84bce817852b7be8a3e1e4a88842860","tid":969161,"uid":23170,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T23:23:34.000Z","msg":"一個10蚊xxxx咪又成堆友走去幫襯，人地根本就無怕過你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T23:42:56.000Z","msg":"根本就係撚狗咁撚<br />\n人地擺明睇你唔起<br />\n但都硬係有班賤過狗嘅人形豬走去食<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d699fa1f4f3d7ea8bfdd3e1281e0b3c1f575a02e","tid":969161,"uid":5995,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T23:56:51.000Z","msg":"今次仲唔到m記員工發威 <br />\n撚狗咁撚你地<br />\n<br />\n利申：唔飲汽水 只飲熱朱<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e8e68689783f6dce96e692b48bce96f93235ae8","tid":969161,"uid":53577,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T00:03:26.000Z","msg":"飲管事件其實係班最下層(低賤)群體突然攞到光環，而自我膨脹。"},{"pid":"6b0928628ae4ab4d2ff453e72d221ea45d555719","tid":969161,"uid":122570,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T00:07:18.000Z","msg":"正宗又要屌又要食 一支飲管都咁撚多人出post 你咪罷食佢囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 真係頂唔順班你班人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n茶記間間都有飲管啦，你地咁有撚嬲咪支持下本地餐廳，罷食到老麥認錯囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13e2bd6e87e252a51a0910ad4d58599bc4a4019e","tid":969161,"uid":39365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T00:09:25.000Z","msg":"我食兩次m記，石陰跟長發既，一問即俾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0111cc85a97ba6449de5746052c0f13a5d47f238","tid":969161,"uid":135840,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime"