f咁撚唔願意比飲管，明撚明你公司寫有需要就可以問佢拎，但啲staff好似無收過呢個order咁一意孤行話唔撚比就唔撚比，仲要好似串鳩你咁<br />\n仆你個臭街我陣間就落去買多個m記食，唔撚比飲管我就小鳩爆佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n多得呢啲人對環保愈黎愈撚反感，遲撚啲我就買包飲管日日連係屋企飲水都用，仆你個臭街"},{"pid":"d682d218f767b4e709920b167de5d5563706acf0","tid":969161,"uid":200771,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T00:46:43.000Z","msg":"橫掂都要環保化，點解m記唔換埋鐵餐具、鐵盤、鐵杯？ 堂食可以循環再造啊...跟本就係想cut cost<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n再唔係可以m記整個塑膠回收箱，洗乾淨哂所有已用餐具(包括膠飲管、膠餐具)  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62a1de0a2170f36197342cd83e8fc4d1cb0b475b","tid":969161,"uid":28279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d682d218f767b4e709920b167de5d5563706acf0","tid":969161,"uid":200771,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T00:46:43.000Z","msg":"橫掂都要環保化，點解m記唔換埋鐵餐具、鐵盤、鐵杯？ 堂食可以循環再造啊...跟本就係想cut cost<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n再唔係可以m記整個塑膠回收箱，洗乾淨哂所有已用餐具(包括膠飲管、膠餐具)  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T00:51:31.000Z","msg":"即係McCafe囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}